{"tid":953704,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"Google 修改 Youtube 的程式碼降低 Edge 的播放效能","createTime":"2018-12-24T06:35:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-24T08:37:01.000Z","uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0d75376a30141eef242875209645f48ef2d3d49f","tid":953704,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T06:35:15.000Z","msg":"Microsoft 於本月宣佈未來其瀏覽器 Edge 將轉使用 Google 開發的 Chromium 為核心，不過今個禮拜卻爆出其中的原因，包含 Google 曾修改 Youtube 的程式碼以降低 Edge 的播放效能。但 Google 就否認此指控。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.xfast-hosting.com/2018/12/Microsoft-edge-chrome-bug-Cover.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.xfast-hosting.com%2F2018%2F12%2FMicrosoft-edge-chrome-bug-Cover.jpg&h=0deb4c62&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n名為 Joshua Bakita 的前微軟實習工程師今個禮拜在 HackerNews 的論壇中指出，他工作的 Edge 部門近日決定終止使用 EdgeHTML 而改用 Chromium，原因之一是 Google 不斷變更旗下網站來破壞其他瀏覽器的運作<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，讓 Microsoft 趕不勝趕<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.xfastest.com/21221/microsoft-charge-google-blow-edge-performance/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.xfastest.com%2F21221%2Fmicrosoft-charge-google-blow-edge-performance%2F&d=s%2BPAoeUTXyRCnWzRG5Mam10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=cb6117a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.xfastest.com/21221/microsoft-charge-google-blow-edge-performance/</a>"},{"pid":"6ca7003a7aab2b8579d41d3bee2f8ca25aabcd32","tid":953704,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T06:35:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79c972144212554496f0e94d1991ea58a9156cc0","tid":953704,"uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T06:36:09.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.xfast-hosting.com/2018/12/edge-youtube-bug.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.xfast-hosting.com%2F2018%2F12%2Fedge-youtube-bug.png&h=21f9cb9e&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n例如 Google 近日為 Youtube 加入空的 div 程式碼，導致 Edge 的硬體加速功能無法啟動 (在 Windows 10 1809 版經已修復) 。在此之前，Edge 以筆電播放影片的電池用電效率其實遠超過 Chrome，但在 Google 動過手腳之後，就一夕翻盤，然後 Google 開始大宣傳 Chrome 播影片的時間完勝 Edge。微軟團隊曾經向 Youtube 要求移除隱藏的空白 div 程式碼，但遭到對方拒絕，而且不再多做解釋。<br />\n<br />\n他並指出，Google 宣稱的完勝不是因為 Chrome 努力提升最佳化，而是因為 Youtube 的跛腳。這點讓人很遺憾。整體而言，他們只有讓網頁跑得更慢。"},{"pid":"9e8dfd1ac613beda6e2381d5cfdd0d01bd5eb4aa","tid":953704,"uid":1886,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T06:37:20.000Z","msg":"Google 方面已透過媒體駁斥上述說法（<a href=\"https://www.theverge.com/2018/12/19/18148736/google-youtube-microsoft-edge-intern-claims\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2018%2F12%2F19%2F18148736%2Fgoogle-youtube-microsoft-edge-intern-claims&d=s%2BPAoeUTXyRCnWzRG5Mam10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=9746cf1a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.theverge.com/2018/12/19/18148736/google-youtube-microsoft-edge-intern-claims</a>）。Google 指出，Youtube 的空白 div 純粹只是一個 bug，在經過通報後就已經解決，Google 並未為了打敗其他瀏覽器而加入任何程式碼。Google 還說經常透過標準組織、Web Platform Tests 專案、Chromium 專案等和其他同業合作。<br />\n<br />\n此事或許也印證不久前 Mozilla 執行長提出的警告，表示在瀏覽器市場微軟打不過 Google 就加入它，將助長 Google 的壟斷。當 Google 透過瀏覽器掌控了絕大多數人使用網際網路的管道，Google 就可能會制訂侵害其他瀏覽器廠商的市場秩序，進而排擠其他廠商生存空間。他說，過去 IE 如此，現在 Google Chrome 也是如此。"},{"pid":"ffe6f5ede10136717d820fe3af86f18098c8d8cc","tid":953704,"uid":130563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T06:42:13.000Z","msg":"微軟自己都有做呢d賤野，有咩資格話人"},{"pid":"f265c963c7543706e35002d8897d3c43f0abf048","tid":953704,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T08:04:39.000Z","msg":"第時啲網站要整多啲空白div"},{"pid":"5d4e687313c51ba2450f7caf4975c26417472b98","tid":953704,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T08:10:10.000Z","msg":"微軟個open xml咪又係加入咗勁多佢專有嘅功能，咁都過到 iso 分明收左錢"},{"pid":"c42d1c289098a6f9d20229294586ca8716f2b2c3","tid":953704,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T08:20:02.000Z","msg":"web browser唔係optimize html效能反而屌人地webpage改code加個div搞到跑分慢左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74675231996f84074e853de64f368fe0bf15e345","tid":953704,"uid":23953,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T08:33:12.000Z","msg":"19 新聞就係鐘意將因果倒返轉咁講<br />\n事實係大部分網站因為要 support IE, 令網站降低 chromium 渲染效能"},{"pid":"1d4125cb2fe39e8bf1b350be5e63c92482ffe887","tid":953704,"uid":48362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T08:34:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3adad6ac8ee28ff4958195e109c4a6d8fba947e2","tid":953704,"uid":23953,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T08:37:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qrEc3mK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqrEc3mK.jpg&h=c39f9e8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMicrosoft: 老子学不动了"}]}